data.title: Czech Republic
data.meta_description: ccb - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The Czech Convention Catalogue provides information on meeting venues, service providers, organizers, caterers and technical suppliers throughout the Czech Republic. It includes over 150 meeting venues ranging from hotels and conference centers to unique locations. The catalog aims to help event organizers find reliable partners to plan conferences, exhibitions, presentations and other events in the Czech Republic.
